#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid "&microbe;"
msgstr "&microbe;"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction and General Syntax"
msgstr "Uvod in splošna sintaksa"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:6
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<application>Microbe</application> compiles programs written in the custom "
"language for PICs, as a companion program to &ktechlab;. The syntax has been "
"designed to suit a &flowcode; program. The syntax for running "
"<command>microbe</command> from the command line is: <programlisting>microbe "
"[options] [input.microbe] [output.asm]</programlisting> where options are:"
msgstr ""
"<application>Microbe</application> prevaja programe, napisane v jeziku po "
"meri za PIC, kot spremljevalni program za &ktechlab;. Sintaksa je bila "
"zasnovana tako, da ustreza &flowcode; programu. Sintaksa za zagon "
"<command>microbe</command> iz ukazne vrstice je: <programlisting>microbe "
"[možnosti] [input.microbe] [output.asm]</programlisting>, kjer so možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>--show-source</function> - Puts each line of &microbe; source code "
"as a comment in the assembly output before the assembly instructions "
"themselves for that line."
msgstr ""
"<function>--show-source</function> - postavi vsako vrstico &microbe; izvorno "
"kodo kot komentar v izhodu sestavljanja pred samimi ukazi zbirnika za to "
"vrstico."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>--no-optimize</function> - Prevent optimization of the "
"instructions generated from the source. Optimization is usually safe, and so "
"this option is mainly used for debugging."
msgstr ""
"<function>--no-optimize</function> – Prepreči optimizacijo ukazov, "
"ustvarjenih iz vira. Optimizacija je običajno varna, zato se ta možnost "
"uporablja predvsem za odpravljanje napak."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The .microbe input file must identify the target PIC by inserting the PIC "
"name at the top of the .microbe file; &eg; the name of a PIC16F84 is "
"\"P16F84\"."
msgstr ""
"Vhodna datoteka .microbe mora identificirati ciljni PIC tako, da vstavi ime "
"PIC na vrh datoteke .microbe; &eg; ime PIC16F84 je \"P16F84\"."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid "Simple complete &microbe; program"
msgstr "Enostavni popoln &microbe; program"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"P16F84\n"
"\n"
"a = 0\n"
"repeat\n"
"{\n"
"        PORTA = a\n"
"        a = a + 1\n"
"}\n"
"until a == 5\n"
"\n"
"end"
msgstr ""
"P16F84\n"
"\n"
"a = 0\n"
"repeat\n"
"{\n"
"        PORTA = a\n"
"        a = a + 1\n"
"}\n"
"until a == 5\n"
"\n"
"end"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "Naming conventions"
msgstr "Pravila poimenovanja"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following rules apply to variable names and labels:"
msgstr "Za imena in oznake spremenljivk veljajo naslednja pravila:"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"They can only contain alphanumerical characters [a..z][A..Z][0..9] and the "
"underscore \"_\"."
msgstr ""
"Vsebujejo lahko samo alfanumerične znake [a..z][A..Z][0..9] in podčrtaj \"_\""

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "They are case-sensitive."
msgstr "Razlikujejo med velikimi in malimi črkami.."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "They cannot start with a number."
msgstr "Ne morejo se začeti s številko."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"They should not start with <quote>__</quote> (double underscore), as this is "
"reserved for use by the compiler."
msgstr ""
"Ne smejo se začeti z <quote>__</quote> (dvojni podčrtaj), saj je to "
"rezervirano za uporabo s strani prevajalnika."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bracing conventions"
msgstr "Konvencije oklepajev"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Curly braces, {}, indicate the start and end of a code block. They can "
"appear anywhere before the start and after the end of the code block. "
"Examples of acceptable code blocks:"
msgstr ""
"Zavita oklepaja, {}, označujeta začetek in konec bloka kode. Lahko se "
"pojavita kjerkoli pred začetkom in po koncu bloka kode. Primeri "
"sprejemljivih kodnih blokov:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"statement1 {\n"
"        some code\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"statement1 {\n"
"        some code\n"
"}"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"statement2 {\n"
"        other code }"
msgstr ""
"statement2 {\n"
"        other code }"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"statement3\n"
"{\n"
"        other code\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"statement3\n"
"{\n"
"        other code\n"
"}"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"statement5 {\n"
"        code block\n"
"} statement6"
msgstr ""
"statement5 {\n"
"        code block\n"
"} statement6"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Commenting"
msgstr "Komentiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Commenting is similar to C. // comments out the rest of the line. /* and */ "
"denote a multiline comment."
msgstr ""
"Komentiranje je podobno C. // komentar v preostaneku vrstice. /* in */"
"označujejo večvrstični komentar."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"// This is a comment\n"
"x = 2 \n"
"/* As is this\n"
"multiline comment */"
msgstr ""
"// This is a comment\n"
"x = 2 \n"
"/* As is this\n"
"multiline comment */"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Program Structure"
msgstr "Struktura programa"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The PIC id must be inserted at the top of the program. The end of the main "
"program is denoted with <quote>end</quote>. Subroutines must placed after "
"<quote>end</quote>."
msgstr ""
"PIC ID mora biti vstavljen na vrh programa. Konec glavnega programa je "
"označen z <quote>end</quote>. Podprogrami morajo biti postavljeni za "
"<quote>end</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Subroutines"
msgstr "Podprogrami"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "A subroutine can be called from anywhere in the code. Syntax:"
msgstr "Podprogram je mogoče poklicati od kjer koli v kodi. Sintaksa:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"sub SubName\n"
"{\n"
"        // Code...\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"sub SubName\n"
"{\n"
"        // Code...\n"
"}"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The subroutine is called with <quote>call <replaceable>SubName</"
"replaceable></quote>."
msgstr ""
"Podprogram se pokliče s <quote>call <replaceable>SubName</replaceable></"
"quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "&microbe; language reference"
msgstr "&microbe; jezikovna referenca"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:85 microbe.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>if</title>"
msgstr "<title>if</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Conditional branching. Syntax: <programlisting role=\"correct\">if "
"[expression] then [statement]</programlisting> or <programlisting role="
"\"correct\">\n"
"if [expression] then\n"
"{\n"
"        [statement block]\n"
"}</programlisting> Similarly for else: <programlisting role=\"correct\">else "
"[statement]</programlisting> or"
msgstr ""
"Pogojno razvejanje. Sintaksa: <programlisting role=\"correct\">if "
"[expression] then [statement]</programlisting> or <programlisting role="
"\"correct\">\n"
"if [expression] then\n"
"{\n"
"        [statement block]\n"
"}</programlisting> Similarly for else: <programlisting role=\"correct\">else "
"[statement]</programlisting> or"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"else\n"
"{\n"
"        [statement block]\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"else\n"
"{\n"
"        [statement block]\n"
"}"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"if porta.0 is high then\n"
"{\n"
"        delay 200\n"
"}\n"
"else\n"
"{\n"
"        delay 300\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"if porta.0 is high then\n"
"{\n"
"        delay 200\n"
"}\n"
"else\n"
"{\n"
"        delay 300\n"
"}"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "alias"
msgstr "vzdevek"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Aliases one string to another. Syntax:"
msgstr "Vzdevek enega niza v drugega. Sintaksa:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "alias [from] [to]"
msgstr "alias [from] [to]"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "repeat"
msgstr "repeat"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Executes the statement block repeatedly until expression evaluates to true. "
"The evaluation of the expression is performed after the statement block, so "
"the statement block will always be executed at least once. Syntax:"
msgstr ""
"Ponavljajoče izvaja blok stavkov, dokler izraz ni ocenjen kot resničen. "
"Vrednotenje izraza se izvede po bloku stavkov, tako da bo blok stavkov vedno "
"izveden vsaj enkrat. Sintaksa:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"repeat\n"
"{\n"
"        [statement block]\n"
"}\n"
"until [expression]"
msgstr ""
"repeat\n"
"{\n"
"        [statement block]\n"
"}\n"
"until [expression]"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "while"
msgstr "while"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similar to repeat, this repeatedly executes the statement block. However, "
"the expression is evaluated before execution, not after. So if the "
"expression evaluates to false on the first pass, then the statement block "
"will not get executed. Syntax:"
msgstr ""
"Podobno kot ponavljanje, to večkrat izvede blok stavkov. Vendar je izraz "
"ovrednoten pred izvedbo, ne po njej. Torej, če je izraz ob prvem prehodu "
"ovrednoten kot false, se blok stavkov ne bo izvedel. Sintaksa:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"while [expression]\n"
"{\n"
"        [statement block]\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"while [expression]\n"
"{\n"
"        [statement block]\n"
"}"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:132 microbe.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "goto"
msgstr "goto"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This causes execution of the code to continue at the next statement after "
"the label specified. Goto syntax: <programlisting role=\"correct"
"\"><function>goto</function> [labelname]</programlisting> Label syntax: "
"<programlisting role=\"correct\"><function>labelname:</function></"
"programlisting> It is often considered good programming practice to avoid "
"the use of goto. Use of control statements and subroutines will result in a "
"much more readable program."
msgstr ""
"To povzroči, da se izvajanje kode nadaljuje pri naslednjem stavku za "
"navedeno oznako. Sintaksa Goto: <programlisting role=\"correct"
"\"><function>goto</function> [labelname]</programlisting> Sintaksa oznake: "
"<programlisting role=\"correct\"><function>labelname:</function></"
"programlisting> Izogibanje uporabi goto se pogosto šteje za dobro programsko "
"prakso. Uporaba kontrolnih stavkov in podprogramov bo povzročila veliko bolj "
"berljiv program."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"goto MyLabel\n"
"\n"
"...\n"
"\n"
"[MyLabel]:\n"
"// Code will continue at this point"
msgstr ""
"goto MyLabel\n"
"\n"
"...\n"
"\n"
"[MyLabel]:\n"
"// Code will continue at this point"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "call"
msgstr "call"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Calls a subroutine. Syntax: <programlisting role=\"correct\"><function>call</"
"function> [SubName]</programlisting> where <replaceable>SubName</"
"replaceable> is the name of the subroutine to be called."
msgstr ""
"Pokliče podprogram. Sintaksa: <programlisting role=\"correct"
"\"><function>call</function> [SubName]</programlisting>, kjer je "
"<replaceable>SubName</replaceable> ime podprograma, ki ga želite poklicati."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "delay"
msgstr "delay"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This causes the code execution to stop for the given period of time. The "
"interval is in milliseconds. Syntax:"
msgstr ""
"To povzroči, da se izvajanje kode ustavi za dano časovno obdobje. Interval "
"je v milisekundah. Sintaksa:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "<function>delay</function> [interval]"
msgstr "<function>delay</function> [interval]"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At present, &microbe; assumes that the PIC is operating at a frequency of "
"4MHz - &ie; each instruction takes 1 microsecond to execute. If this is not "
"the case, the interval must be adjusted proportionately."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno &microbe; predpostavlja, da PIC deluje na frekvenci 4MHz - &ie; "
"vsako navodilo traja 1 mikrosekundo za izvedbo. Če temu ni tako, je treba "
"interval sorazmerno prilagoditi."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "sevenseg"
msgstr "sevenseg"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used to define the pin mapping for a (common cathode) seven segment "
"display connected to the PIC. Syntax: <programlisting role=\"correct"
"\"><function>sevenseg</function> [name] [a] [b] [c] [d] [e] [f] [g]</"
"programlisting> where [a]...[g] are the PIC pins to which the respective "
"segments of the seven segment display are attached. The pins can be written "
"either as PORTX.N or RXN."
msgstr ""
"To se uporablja za definiranje preslikave nogic za katodni sedemsegmentni "
"zaslon (s skupno katodo), povezan s PIC. Sintaksa: <programlisting role="
"\"correct\"><function>sevenseg</function> [ime] [a] [b] [c] [d] [e] [f] [g]</"
"programlisting> kjer je [a] ...[g] so nogice PIC, na katere so pritrjeni "
"ustrezni segmenti sedemsegmentnega zaslona. Nogice so lahko zapisane kot "
"PORTX.N ali RXN."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To display a number on the seven segment, the pin mapping is treated as a "
"write only variable."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz številke na segmentu sedmih se preslikava nogice obravnava kot "
"spremenljivka samo za pisanje."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Defining and outputting to a seven segment"
msgstr "Definiranje in izpis v sedem segmentov"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"sevenseg seg1 RB0 RB1 RB2 RB3 RB4 RB5 RB6\n"
"seg1 = x + 2"
msgstr ""
"sevenseg seg1 RB0 RB1 RB2 RB3 RB4 RB5 RB6\n"
"seg1 = x + 2"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "keypad"
msgstr "keypad"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used to define the pin mapping for a keypad connected to the PIC. "
"Syntax: <programlisting role=\"correct\"><function>keypad</function> [name] "
"[row 1] ... [row 4] [column 1] ... [column n]</programlisting> where [row "
"1] ... [row 4] and [column 1] ... [column n] are the PIC pins to which the "
"respective rows and columns of the keypad are attached (at the moment, the "
"number of rows is not changeable). See <xref linkend=\"sevenseg\"/> (above) "
"for more information on pin mappings."
msgstr ""
"To se uporablja za definiranje preslikave nogic za tipkovnico, povezano s "
"PIC. Sintaksa: <programlisting role=\"correct\"><function>keypad</function> "
"[ime] [vrstica 1] ... [vrstica 4] [stolpec 1] ... [stolpec n]</"
"programlisting> kjer [vrstica 1] ... [vrstica 4] in [stolpec 1] ... [stolpec "
"n] so nogice PIC, na katere so pritrjene ustrezne vrstice in stolpci "
"tipkovnice (trenutno število vrstic ni spremenljivo) . Glejte <xref linkend="
"\"sevenseg\"/> (zgoraj) za več informacij o preslikavah nogic."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The columns of the keypad should be pulled down via 100k resistors to "
"ground. The row pins must be configured as outputs and the column pins as "
"inputs. Once the keypad has been defined, it is treated as a read only "
"variable."
msgstr ""
"Stolpce tipkovnice je treba potegniti navzdol preko 100k uporov na maso. "
"Nogice vrstic morajo biti konfigurirane kot izhodi, nogice stolpcev pa kot "
"vhodi. Ko je tipkovnica definirana, se obravnava kot spremenljivka samo za "
"branje."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Defining and reading from a keypad"
msgstr "Definiranje in branje s tipkovnice"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"keypad keypad1 RB0 RB1 RB2 RB3 RB4 RB5 RB6\n"
"x = keypad1"
msgstr ""
"keypad keypad1 RB0 RB1 RB2 RB3 RB4 RB5 RB6\n"
"x = keypad1"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, the values returned for a keypad are: <itemizedlist> "
"<listitem><para>The value of the number if it is a numeric key (1 to 3 along "
"top row; hexadecimal A to D down the fourth column and continuing for each "
"extra column).</para></listitem> <listitem><para>253 for the key in row 4, "
"column 1.</para></listitem> <listitem><para>254 for the key in row 4, column "
"3.</para></listitem> </itemizedlist> These values can be redefined by using "
"the alias command, where the name of the key in row x, column y (rows and "
"columns starting at 1), is Keypad_x_y. For example, to give the star key on "
"a 4x3 keypad the value zero, the following alias would be used:"
msgstr ""
"Privzeto so vrnjene vrednosti za tipkovnico: <itemizedlist> "
"<listitem><para>Vrednost številke, če je številska tipka (1 do 3 v zgornji "
"vrstici; šestnajstiški A do D navzdol v četrtem stolpcu in nadaljevanje za "
"vsak dodatni stolpec).</para></listitem> <listitem><para>253 za tipko v "
"vrstici 4, stolpec 1.</para></listitem> <listitem><para>254 za tipko v "
"vrstici 4, stolpec 3.</para></listitem> </itemizedlist> Te vrednosti je "
"mogoče na novo definirati z uporabo ukaza alias, kjer je ime tipke v vrstici "
"x, stolpcu y (vrstice in stolpci, ki se začnejo pri 1), Keypad_x_y. Če "
"želite na primer tipki zvezdica na tipkovnici 4x3 dati vrednost nič, bi "
"uporabili naslednji vzdevek:"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Aliasing a keypad key to a value"
msgstr "Določanje vzdevka tipke na tipkovnici za vrednost"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "alias Keypad_4_1 0"
msgstr "alias Keypad_4_1 0"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "PIC I/O"
msgstr "PIC I/O"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Port Direction"
msgstr "Smer vrat"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The port direction is set by assigning a value to TRIS*, where * is the port "
"letter. For example:"
msgstr ""
"Smer vrat se nastavi tako, da se TRIS* dodeli vrednost, kjer je * črka vrat. "
"Na primer:"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting port directions"
msgstr "Nastavitev smeri vrat"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "TRISB = b'01111001'"
msgstr "TRISB = b'01111001'"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The above sets pins RB1, RB2 and RB7 on PORTB as outputs, and the other pins "
"on PORTB as inputs. In this example, b'01111001' is a binary representation "
"of the output type. The 1 on the right represents an output on RB0, and the "
"0 on the left represents an input on RB7."
msgstr ""
"Zgornje nastavi nogice RB1, RB2 in RB7 na PORTB kot izhode, druge nogice na "
"PORTB pa kot vhode. V tem primeru je b'01111001' binarna predstavitev vrste "
"izhoda. 1 na desni predstavlja izhod na RB0, 0 na levi pa vhod na RB7."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Port I/O"
msgstr "Vrata I/O"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "The port can be treated as a variable. For example:"
msgstr "Vrata je mogoče obravnavati kot spremenljivko. Na primer:"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid "Writing to a port"
msgstr "Pisanje na vrata"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "x = PORTA"
msgstr "x = PORTA"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "The above assigns the value of PORTA to the variable x."
msgstr "Zgornje dodeljuje vrednost PORTA spremenljivki x."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pin I/O"
msgstr "Pin I/O"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each pin on a port is obtained by prefixing the pin number by the port name; "
"&eg; Pin 2 (starting from Pin 0) on PORTA is known as <emphasis>PORTA.0</"
"emphasis>. The syntax to set a pin state is: <programlisting role=\"correct"
"\">PORTX.N = <emphasis>STATE</emphasis></programlisting> where "
"<emphasis>STATE</emphasis> can be <emphasis>high</emphasis> or "
"<emphasis>low</emphasis>. The syntax to test a pin state is: <programlisting "
"role=\"correct\"><function>if</function> PORTX.N is <emphasis>STATE</"
"emphasis> <function>then</function></programlisting> Combining these "
"examples, we have:"
msgstr ""
"Vsako nogico na vratih dobimo tako, da pred številko nogice dodamo ime vrat; "
"&eg; Pin 2 (začenši z nogico 0) na PORTA je znan kot <emphasis>PORTA.0</"
"emphasis>. Sintaksa za nastavitev stanja nogice je: <programlisting role="
"\"correct\">PORTX.N = <emphasis>STATE</emphasis></programlisting>, kjer je "
"<emphasis>STATE</emphasis> lahko <emphasis>high</emphasis> ali "
"<emphasis>low</emphasis>. Sintaksa za preizkus stanja nogice je: "
"<programlisting role=\"correct\"><function>if</function> PORTX.N je "
"<emphasis>STATE</emphasis> <function>then</function></programlisting> S "
"kombiniranjem teh primerov imamo:"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting and testing pin state"
msgstr "Nastavitev in testiranje stanja nogice"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"TRISA = 0\n"
"TRISB = 255\n"
"<function>if</function> PORTA.3 is <function>high</function> <function>then</"
"function>\n"
"{\n"
"        PORTB.5 = <function>low</function>\n"
"}\n"
"<function>else</function>\n"
"{\n"
"        PORTB = PORTA + 15\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"TRISA = 0\n"
"TRISB = 255\n"
"<function>if</function> PORTA.3 is <function>high</function> <function>then</"
"function>\n"
"{\n"
"        PORTB.5 = <function>low</function>\n"
"}\n"
"<function>else</function>\n"
"{\n"
"        PORTB = PORTA + 15\n"
"}"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "Variables"
msgstr "Spremenljivke"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All variables are 8-bit unsigned integers, giving a range from 0 to 255. "
"<application>&microbe;</application> supports the typical unary operations "
"(acting on one variable) and binary operations (acting on two variables) "
"that are supported by the PIC. In addition, &microbe; also supports division "
"and multiplication."
msgstr ""
"Vse spremenljivke so 8-bitna nepredznačena cela števila, ki v obsegu od 0 do "
"255. <application>&microbe;</application> podpira tipične unarne operacije "
"(delujejo na eno spremenljivko) in binarne operacije (delujejo na dve "
"spremenljivki), ki jih podpira PIC. Poleg tega &microbe; podpira tudi "
"deljenje in množenje."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unary Operations"
msgstr "Unarne operacije"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>rotateleft x</emphasis> - Rotates the variable x left through "
"carry."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>rotateleft x</emphasis> – Zasuka spremenljivko x levo skozi prenos."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>rotateright x</emphasis> - Rotates the variable x right through "
"carry."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>rotateright x</emphasis> – Zasuka spremenljivko x desno skozi "
"prenos."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>increment x</emphasis> - Increments the variable x. If x has a "
"value of 255, then x wraps round to 0."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>inkrement x</emphasis> – Poveča spremenljivko x. Če ima x vrednost "
"255, se x zaokroži na 0."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>decrement x</emphasis> - Decrements the variable x. If x has a "
"value of 0, then x wraps round to 255."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>zmanjšaj x</emphasis> – Zmanjša spremenljivko x. Če ima x vrednost "
"0, se x zaokroži na 255."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arithmetic"
msgstr "Aritmetika"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:293 microbe.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Supported operations:"
msgstr "Podprte operacije:"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Addition:</emphasis> x + y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Seštevanje:</emphasis> x + y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Subtraction:</emphasis> x - y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Odštevanje:</emphasis> x - y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Multiplication:</emphasis> x * y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Množenje:</emphasis> x * y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Division:</emphasis> x / y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Deljenje:</emphasis> x / y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Binary XOR:</emphasis> x XOR y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Binarni XOR:</emphasis> x XOR y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Binary AND:</emphasis> x AND y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Binarni AND:</emphasis> x AND y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Binary OR:</emphasis> x OR y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Binarni OR:</emphasis> x OR y"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:308 microbe.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comparison"
msgstr "Primerjava"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Equals:</emphasis> x == y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Enakost:</emphasis> x == y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Does not equal:</emphasis> x != y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Neenakost:</emphasis> x != y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Is greater than:</emphasis> x > y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Je večje od:</emphasis> x > y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Is less than:</emphasis> x &lt; y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Je manjše kot:</emphasis> x &lt; l"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Is greater than or equal to:</emphasis> x &gt;= y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Je večje ali enako:</emphasis> x &gt;= y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Is less than or equal to:</emphasis> x &lt;= y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Je manjše ali enako:</emphasis> x &lt;= y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "For example:"
msgstr "Na primer:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>if</function> PORTA >= 5 <function>then</function>\n"
"{\n"
"        ...\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"<function>if</function> PORTA >= 5 <function>then</function>\n"
"{\n"
"        ...\n"
"}"
